CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 14, 1962, pg. 11 reads: "Teeing Off - Five members of the Green Links Golf Club got together to practice, in preparation for the club's golf tournament at North Park on July 22. Watching Gloria Grate, club president, tee off are (Left to right) Lorraine Tillman, Louise Hinton, Helen Peay and Maude Jones. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Five members of the Green Link Golf Club, from left: Louise Hinton, Kathleen Fitts, Maude Jones, possibly Lorraine Tillman, and Gloria Golden Grate, posed at Schenley Park golf course, another version
